  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You'll receive a fruit basket in your room on arrival and the in-room tea and coffee facilities are replenished daily.</p>
<p>The hotel's delicious buffet breakfast has a large range of both hot and cold items and a juice bar where you can make your own fruit and vegetable juice.</p>
<p>The three course evening meal features Swiss cuisine (fondue is available!) and there is a choice of main course. One two days of the week, the half board meal is taken in the sister <a data-udi="umb://document/b9f7c9e30df74309a68c7482d3814476" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b9f7c9e30df74309a68c7482d3814476}" title="Hotel Schönegg">Hotel Schönegg</a>.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
