  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spa &amp; wellness facilities</strong></p>
<p>400m² wellness area with an indoor swimming pool and spa with two saunas, steam room, sensory showers and relaxation room. Please note that the spa area is reserved for adults only and is garment free. After 8pm the pool is for adults only.</p>
<ul>
<li>Swimming pool</li>
<li>Whirlpool</li>
<li>Finnish sauna</li>
<li>Hay sauna</li>
<li>Steam room</li>
<li>'Sensory' shower</li>
<li>Relaxation room</li>
<li>Gym</li>
<li>Beauty and massage treatments (payable locally)</li>
<li>Pool towels</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Additional facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Terrace</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cots and linen</li>
<li>Early meals available from 6pm</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
