  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This friendly and welcoming hotel offers excellent service, delicious meals, and a luxurious swimming pool and spa area. All rooms have sunny, south-facing balconies which offer the perfect place to enjoy the views. An easy walk from the town centre, the hotel is opposite the Sunnegga funicular, giving easy access to the mountains and walking trails.</p>]]></listingDescription>
